a few hundred a year...

95
00:09:20,267 --> 00:09:22,687
<i>Can it build about two apartment buildings?</i>

96
00:09:22,688 --> 00:09:24,817
What a pathetic kid.
Hey, Yeon Hee.

97
00:09:24,818 --> 00:09:26,614
- Yeah, Danny.
- Pour me a drink.

98
00:09:26,812 --> 00:09:27,960
Okay.

99
00:09:27,961 --> 00:09:30,327
Chae Do Woo.
Might as well come out with it.

100
00:09:30,328 --> 00:09:33,059
I heard a rumor that
you messed with Byukjaewon.

101
00:09:33,064 --> 00:09:35,533
<i>- It's about that, right?
- What's Byukjaewon?</i>

102
00:09:35,813 --> 00:09:38,503
You don't know? It's that company
that sells tofu and dumplings.

103
00:09:38,504 --> 00:09:41,534
Because of the dumpling scandal,
their stock price fell.

104
00:09:42,802 --> 00:09:46,139
I heard there was someone who shook it up.
Was it you, Do Woo?

105
00:09:47,861 --> 00:09:50,755
What's with this childish act?
Tofu and dumplings?

106
00:09:51,059 --> 00:09:54,103
It's pretty big.
Its revenue is in the tens of billions.

107
00:09:58,704 --> 00:10:01,989
Everything's been planned out.
I just need to hit it a couple more times.

108
00:10:01,990 --> 00:10:05,515
You bastard.
So you're going to take over a company...

109
00:10:05,516 --> 00:10:08,187
and you were thinking of
giving us the interest?

110
00:10:10,164 --> 00:10:13,971
Since it's risky,
I'll take in the risk first...

111
00:10:13,972 --> 00:10:15,497
Drink.

112
00:10:15,498 --> 00:10:18,392
- How many shots is this?
- Thirteen.

113
