the maximum is up to 30 billion Won.

126
00:11:37,343 --> 00:11:39,948
- Do Woo.
- Yeah.

127
00:11:40,540 --> 00:11:42,176
Drink.

128
00:12:01,692 --> 00:12:03,044
Do Woo.

129
00:12:05,216 --> 00:12:06,400
I'll drink it.

130
