141
00:12:57,271 --> 00:12:59,452
<i>- Director Oh!
- Yeah.</i>

142
00:12:59,453 --> 00:13:02,542
- Take care of my son...
- Okay, I'll take care of it. Go home.

143
00:13:09,888 --> 00:13:11,214
