153
00:13:55,525 --> 00:13:59,460
You... scary bastard.
How did you know about that?

154
00:14:01,227 --> 00:14:04,926
One month from Friday.
Doesn't matter when it goes out.

155
00:14:07,026 --> 00:14:09,167
I won't take a cent
of what you invested.

156
00:14:09,627 --> 00:14:13,063
You'll give us 100 to 300 percent
in profit margin?

157
00:14:25,490 --> 00:14:28,398
