a little more than 2 billion Won.

160
00:14:36,263 --> 00:14:39,292
What?
I had something like that?

161
00:14:39,293 --> 00:14:41,800
The inheritance you got two years ago
pays off tomorrow.

162
00:14:41,801 --> 00:14:44,806
You slick bastard.

163
00:14:44,807 --> 00:14:47,986
How do you know about the stock
I didn't even know I had?

164
00:14:49,174 --> 00:14:52,057
