Want in?

165
00:14:53,066 --> 00:14:55,150
Okay. I'm in.

166
00:14:55,958 --> 00:14:59,282
To be honest, Danny only knows
how to spend money.

167
00:14:59,719 --> 00:15:04,387
I'll invest in you.
Because you only know how to earn money.

168
00:15:05,716 --> 00:15:07,088
Me?

169
00:15:07,692 --> 00:15:10,610
