He's well.

175
00:15:51,620 --> 00:15:53,662
<i>Ahh.</i>

176
00:15:57,688 --> 00:15:59,226
Ah, ah.

177
00:16:38,072 --> 00:16:39,138
2924.

178
00:16:41,876 --> 00:16:43,328
<i>Let's go.</i>

179
00:16:43,329 --> 00:16:46,031
- Please put me in another room.
- What?

180
00:16:47,621 --> 00:16:50,927
If I go back, I'm going to die in that
room. So please place me in another room.

181
00:16:51,334 --> 00:16:53,520
