a written explanation.

182
00:16:53,521 --> 00:16:57,307
So... please put me in a different room.

183
00:17:00,854 --> 00:17:02,469
Come inside.

184
00:17:40,485 --> 00:17:41,689
Hey, you.

185
00:17:46,393 --> 00:17:47,589
You there.

186
00:17:50,014 --> 00:17:51,898
You're not with those gangsters, right?

187
00:17:56,524 --> 00:17:58,310
