188
00:17:58,311 --> 00:18:00,786
Those bastards just leave you be.

189
00:18:05,381 --> 00:18:07,054
Has it been long since you've been here?

190
00:18:07,055 --> 00:18:09,746
So is that why...
you know some tricks?

191
00:18:11,633 --> 00:18:14,818
Look here.
Teach me.

192
00:18:14,819 --> 00:18:16,561
