to those bastards?

193
00:18:16,562 --> 00:18:20,343
No... I just want to change rooms.
How do I do that?

194
00:18:20,344 --> 00:18:23,073
What do I have to do?

195
00:18:32,914 --> 00:18:37,232
Why am I asking a crazy gangster...

196
00:18:38,968 --> 00:18:42,404
