199
00:19:02,497 --> 00:19:04,993
they've asked me to put in a lot.

200
00:19:07,271 --> 00:19:09,911
Money.
And food.

201
00:19:09,912 --> 00:19:12,284
Along with brand name training clothes.

202
00:19:13,205 --> 00:19:14,913
Of many different sizes.

203
00:19:16,153 --> 00:19:17,929
They ask me to put in a lot.

204
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:20,099
When people come to visit, they say it.

205
00:19:20,895 --> 00:19:22,171
To put in a lot for them.

206
00:19:23,618 --> 00:19:25,278
That's all you need.

207
00:19:26,413 --> 00:19:28,617
Money...
Money...

208
00:19:28,618 --> 00:19:30,630
Money.

209
00:19:35,578 --> 00:19:37,136
<i>Don't come.</i>

210
00:19:38,122 --> 00:19:40,099
You mustn't come.

211
00:19:40,510 --> 00:19:43,375
You know the money at home?
Take that and leave for someplace far away.

212
00:19:43,376 --> 00:19:45,595
Don't even tell me where you're going!

213
00:19:46,281 --> 00:19:49,901
These guys are ten times worse
than the gangsters last time...

214
00:19:49,902 --> 00:19:51,506
If they find out about you Myung Sun...

215
00:19:52,166 --> 00:19:54,409
they might even harass your family.

216
00:19:55,478 --> 00:19:58,143
Shin... but...

217
00:19:58,144 --> 00:19:59,835
From now on...

218
00:19:59,836 --> 00:20:02,384
