don't even think about me either.

225
00:20:26,514 --> 00:20:28,492
Just do as I tell you!

226
00:21:09,802 --> 00:21:12,138
<i>It's been over a week since they've moved.</i>

227
00:21:12,835 --> 00:21:15,392
<i>They basically sold off
their furniture or whatever...</i>

228
00:21:15,393 --> 00:21:19,954
<i>At dawn, they rented a moving van,
packed their things and left.</i>

229
00:21:20,941 --> 00:21:23,318
<i>Aren't you Shin's fiancee?</i>

230
00:21:24,566 --> 00:21:25,930
