241
00:22:00,343 --> 00:22:02,214
<i>I hear a lot of things.</i>

242
00:22:02,748 --> 00:22:06,372
That's right. I cut ties off with them
but now I want to repair them.

243
00:22:06,373 --> 00:22:08,921
